%o A397701 (PARI) isok(k) = {my(f = factor(k)); sigma(f) == prod(i=1, #f~, (f[i, 1]+1) * f[i, 1]^(f[i, 2]-1)) + numdiv(f)^3 + omega(f)^3; } \\ _Amiram Eldar_, Jul 05 2026
